DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260309T203000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260309T205000
SUMMARY:Inner Body Meditation (20 minutes)
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\n"Awareness of the inner body takes you bey
 ond the mind." - Eckhart Tolle\n\nIn this mediation session we will bring 
 our attention here: to the inner body. Sessions are suitable for newcomers
 \, those experienced in Tolle's teachings and anyone wishing to remain com
 pletely anonymous. They will last around 20 minutes and cameras and microp
 hones will be disabled.\n(Depending on the situation\, a free discussion m
 ay be held at the end with mics and cameras allowed.)\n\nSee you there!\n\
 nPlease be aware that sessions will close if no members have joined after 
 10 minutes.\n\nEmrys also organises a free Work of Byron Katie online medi
 ation group. Visit [this Meetup Group link](https://www.meetup.com/thework
