BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313423480@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260305T024123Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260310T213000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260310T223000
SUMMARY:Awakening Awareness: Embracing This Moment
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\nFeel free to join as we get still and prac
 tise presence within this moment. We will discuss and observe the obstacle
 s that\, seemingly\, block us from being present and bring awareness to ou
 r unconsciousness in a safe\, inclusive and affirming way.\n\nSessions are
  suitable for newcomers\, those experienced in Tolle's teaching and anyone
  wishing to remain completely anonymous.\n\nSee you there!\n\nPlease be aw
 are that sessions will close if no members have joined after 10 minutes.\n
 \nEmrys has been passionate about mindfulness since 2010 and since 2021 he
  has been organising free\, weekly online meditation groups. For more info
 rmation on his free Work of Byron Katie online mediation group\, visit [th
 is Meetup Group link](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/themindfulstream/events/313423480/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260219T022517Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260219T022517Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313440009@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260305T024123Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260311T213000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260311T223000
SUMMARY:Beginners in The Work of Byron Katie: Newcomers Welcome
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\nTo RSVP\, please [click here](https://dash
 board.mailerlite.com/forms/1073947/134679151955150756/share). Guests must 
 complete a contact form and the Zoom link will be sent to by email. Thank 
 you.\n\nA free Zoom meditation session designed with newcomers in mind. Se
 ssions will include at least one hour of facilitation (meditation) and the
 re is room for questions and answers throughout. If you're curious about T
 he Work\, you're invited to join!\n\nSee you there!\n\nPlease be aware tha
 t sessions will close if no members have joined after 10 minutes.\n\n**To 
 book a free introductory private session with Emrys\, [click here](https:/
 /calendly.com/mindfulnesswithemrys/onehoursession)[.](https://mindfulnessw
 ithemrys.business.site/)**\n\nEmrys also organises a free Work of Byron Ka
 tie Meetup group. Visit: [https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree](https:/
 /www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/)\n\n*Find out more about Emrys [here](ht
 tps://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)[.](http://linktr.ee/theworkruns
 free)*\n\nTo best prepare for each session\, complete a *Judge Your Neighb
 our* worksheet free at [https://thework.com/part-three/](https://thework.c
 om/part-three/) or visit [http://www.thework.com](http://www.thework.com)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/themindfulstream/events/313440009/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260220T022101Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260220T022101Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
